        {
            "title": "德股低收約1.8%本周升2%  奢侈品急挫",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐洲主要股市收市下跌。泛歐指數Stoxx 600收市回吐0.46%，報553點，早段一度滑落0.98%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：德國證交所官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250306_FI_source-web_eu-stock-1-1.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：德國證交所官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250306_FI_source-web_eu-stock-1-1.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：德國證交所官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">受累美國關稅政策，市場憂慮奢侈品銷售表現受影響，相關股份受壓，歷峰集團(Richemont)股價急挫5.4%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">德國DAX指數報23008點，跌410點，跌幅約1.8%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">法國CAC指數報8120點，跌76點，跌幅0.9%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國富時100指數報8679點，跌2點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">意大利富時MIB指數收報38592點，回落0.48%或186點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">西班牙IBEX 35指數收報13257點，反彈0.17%或22點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">全星期計，德股累計上升2%，法股升0.1%，英股跌近1.5%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14760979-%e5%be%b7%e8%82%a1%e4%bd%8e%e6%94%b6%e7%b4%841-8%e6%9c%ac%e5%91%a8%e5%8d%872-%e5%a5%a2%e4%be%88%e5%93%81%e6%80%a5%e6%8c%ab",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250306_FI_source-web_eu-stock-2.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-08 10:20:51",
