        {
            "title": "王國龍減領展100萬單位   套現3646萬元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港交所(00388)股權披露顯示，領展(00823)行政總裁王國龍於今年3月6日在場內沽出100萬個領展單位，每單位平均作價36.4624元，套現逾3646萬元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：領展官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20231108_FI_source-web_00823.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：領展官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20231108_FI_source-web_00823.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：領展官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">王國龍持有領展股權，將由0.2%減至0.16%或約430.12萬股。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">王國龍對上一次在場內減持，是2023年8月，當時減持逾107萬個單位，每股平均價為42.39元，套現逾4500萬元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14760067-%e7%8e%8b%e5%9c%8b%e9%be%8d%e6%b8%9b%e9%a0%98%e5%b1%95100%e8%90%ac%e5%96%ae%e4%bd%8d-%e5%a5%97%e7%8f%be3646%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/00823.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-07 18:10:58",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
